🚨 Incident Simulation Scenarios

This lab includes simulated real-world incidents:

  1. Unauthorized Access Attempt
    • Triggered multiple failed login attempts
    • Alert generated via Azure Monitor
    • Logs analyzed in SIEM
  2. IAM Misconfiguration
    • Over-permissioned user account
    • Identified and corrected using RBAC
  3. Network Anomaly
    • Simulated blocked traffic via NSG rules
    • Diagnosed connectivity issue (DNS/VPN)
  4. VM Performance Issue
    • High CPU utilization alert triggered
    • Investigated and resolved performance bottleneck

